<p>Behat will call this method one time, even if we're testing 10 features and 100 scenarios.</p>
<h2 id="saving-a-new-user">Saving a New User <a class="headerlink" href="control-database#saving-a-new-user" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Inside of the<code>thereIsAnAdminUserWithPassword()</code> step definition, let's go to work!
I already have a <code>User</code> entity setup in the project, so we can say <code>$user = new User()</code>.
Then set the username and the "plainPassword":</p>
