<p>I have a Doctrine listener already setup that will encode the password automatically.
Which is good: it's well-known that raptors can smell un-encoded passwords...</p>
<p>In this app, to make this an "admin" user, we need to give the user <code>ROLE_ADMIN</code>:</p>
